Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.93,0:00:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.21,0:00:20.05,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Newdays 開始的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.12,0:00:23.02,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,給世界一個吻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.49,0:00:26.15,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Blowing in thewind
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.22,0:00:31.72,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,把一點點的勇氣和愛放進口袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.80,0:00:40.36,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,l wish如果我有翅膀的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.20,0:00:50.20,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,不管悲傷、過去還是不安 都能夠飛越
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.28,0:00:52.27,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,OhYeah！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.35,0:00:56.68,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有失去什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.25,0:01:01.15,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemyway！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.22,0:01:04.09,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,想用這掌心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.16,0:01:07.36,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,抓住奇蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.33,0:01:16.36,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,朝向無盡的天空和大地 以及未來旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.17,0:01:20.37,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,剛長出的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.44,0:01:23.57,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh！ 一定一定一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.65,0:01:24.84,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.91,0:01:28.37,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,展現光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.12,0:01:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過還真是令人吃驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.82,0:01:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說有龍？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.72,0:01:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是有人目擊到外形像龍的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.89,0:01:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過更應該注意的是跟牠戰鬥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.06,0:01:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某種人型物體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.50,0:01:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你認為那是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.67,0:01:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秩序守護者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是屬下個人的看法...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.44,0:01:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還一直以為史達姆少校\N是個很徹底的現實主義者呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.71,0:01:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.01,0:02:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂．卡蘇魯打倒了那個東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.28,0:02:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事不能當作沒看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.19,0:02:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是置之不理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.49,0:02:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概會不斷出現\N想得到那股力量的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.59,0:02:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在其實已經...\N基亞特帝國第三公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.56,0:02:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽內絲露露基亞特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.20,0:02:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得她率領的危機管理組織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.73,0:02:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像叫"緋紅"吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.17,0:02:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.47,0:02:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其這兩年來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.47,0:02:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緋紅的奇特行動相當引人注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.71,0:02:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叛亂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.01,0:02:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有這個可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.71,0:02:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為廢棄公主和她身邊的一行人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.88,0:02:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有足夠的力量\N一口氣破壞這個世界的勢力平衡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.02,0:02:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.29,0:02:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，史達姆少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.23,0:02:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#07 流浪少女的圓舞曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.75,0:03:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個變成怪物的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.31,0:03:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不直接衝著我來呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.19,0:03:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔爾斯鎮那時候也是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.96,0:03:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要殺我的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.59,0:03:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接衝著我來不就好了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.76,0:03:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.34,0:03:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.30,0:03:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有敵人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.14,0:03:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.21,0:03:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.81,0:03:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼偏偏在這種地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.58,0:03:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有什麼辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.08,0:03:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.08,0:03:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠馬車移動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.52,0:03:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來差不多是極限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.29,0:03:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旅費也快要見底了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.02,0:03:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許是該好好想想的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.27,0:04:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要弄壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.21,0:04:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡沒人住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.04,0:04:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這房子用來避雨應該沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.21,0:04:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來要在這裡待一陣子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.75,0:04:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼夏儂哥，事情就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.65,0:04:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是要去買東西嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.12,0:04:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.36,0:04:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鹽漬食品、生蔥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.79,0:04:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬鈴薯、雞蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.40,0:04:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有內衣兩件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.97,0:04:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒有忘記要買的東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.70,0:04:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過真是個\N超愛亂使喚哥哥的老妹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.97,0:05:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.75,0:05:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說妳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這樣豈不是讓我像個傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.49,0:05:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫...詩音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.39,0:05:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，妳叫詩音啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.72,0:05:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音妳聽好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.16,0:05:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在旅行途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.86,0:05:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以跟著我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.10,0:05:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懂嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.77,0:05:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.56,0:06:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.83,0:06:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉蔻兒姊我問妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.63,0:06:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼拉蔻兒姊會用魔法呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.00,0:06:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛...為什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.90,0:06:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼卻一直在用嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.37,0:06:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔法是一種靠感覺的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.04,0:06:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以很難用言語來說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.48,0:06:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，媽媽說過這股力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.51,0:06:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是依據人的意識容量大小而定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.32,0:06:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,容量？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.49,0:06:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話雖然這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.35,0:06:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過也不是容量大\N就什麼事都做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.46,0:06:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.59,0:06:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.16,0:06:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔法這種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.36,0:06:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是讓原有的自然力量\N交互作用而發生的現象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.34,0:06:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.14,0:06:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.47,0:06:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男爵夫人，請問有何指示？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.43,0:07:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是見外啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.90,0:07:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不叫我母親大人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑就到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.60,0:07:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進入正題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.87,0:07:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你去聖都葛林德一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.77,0:07:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於第5111次的\N聖葛林德神諭，是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，你真是一點就通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.45,0:07:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.68,0:07:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就先告退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.68,0:07:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.26,0:07:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寄件人好像叫薇妮雅切斯特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.73,0:07:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薇妮雅？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.33,0:07:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會有女孩子寫信給克里斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.97,0:07:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是太感動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.27,0:07:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果我就把這封信放在傳閱板上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.61,0:08:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在部隊裡四處傳閱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.37,0:08:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男爵夫人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.84,0:08:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驚爆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.28,0:08:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個克里斯多福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.55,0:08:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有個年紀比他大的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.55,0:08:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女朋友嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.48,0:08:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.02,0:08:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,內容雖然是\N沒什麼大不了的感謝信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.09,0:08:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我能感覺到在文字背後\N隱藏著一份少女的思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.46,0:08:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您解析得還真是深入啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.26,0:08:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為對我這種\N閒得發慌的貴婦人來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.00,0:08:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別人的戀愛故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.40,0:08:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是最好的娛樂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.77,0:08:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種話請您不要自己這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.91,0:08:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.81,0:08:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的地是聖都葛林德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.91,0:08:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可以去找薇妮雅喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.95,0:08:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.42,0:08:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要拿這孩子怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.45,0:08:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算妳問我，我也不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.86,0:08:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是也還不能確定\N這孩子是不是孤兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.79,0:08:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定這是犯法的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.76,0:08:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且以我們的處境來說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.00,0:09:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都知道，可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.91,0:09:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被這雙眼睛一看\N我就什麼也說不出口了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.38,0:09:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.65,0:09:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不說清楚一點怎麼行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.42,0:09:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何況我們又不能帶著她一起走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.22,0:09:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼比平常還要嚴厲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.19,0:09:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然是因為...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.62,0:09:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂你帶了一個女孩子回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.63,0:09:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我平常就很嚴厲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.73,0:09:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.76,0:09:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.38,0:09:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...詩音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.28,0:09:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能跟妳在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.28,0:09:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳懂嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.85,0:09:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.49,0:09:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得跟妳說再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.89,0:09:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.49,0:09:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，妳被討厭了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.19,0:10:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要光笑，拉蔻兒姊也說句話啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.13,0:10:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...詩音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.68,0:10:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音妳想要怎麼做呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.95,0:10:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音有家嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.45,0:10:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.45,0:10:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.59,0:10:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳有沒有爸爸還是媽媽呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.39,0:10:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.89,0:10:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟他們走散了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.69,0:10:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是說都過世了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.80,0:10:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說妳什麼都不記得了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.01,0:10:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天就先讓她留在這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.34,0:10:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚了總不能把她趕出去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.34,0:11:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.68,0:11:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.85,0:11:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.39,0:11:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.19,0:11:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算想硬把詩音送回鎮上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.19,0:11:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看他們那個樣子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.73,0:11:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話是沒錯啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.90,0:11:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了，反正我們一開始就打算\N在這裡至少待個四、五天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.93,0:11:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.17,0:11:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳就把夏儂借給詩音吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.84,0:11:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這是什麼意思啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.71,0:11:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在嘀咕些什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.77,0:11:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.21,0:11:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音，妳一直黏著夏儂哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.04,0:11:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他這種人哪裡好啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.88,0:12:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.95,0:12:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.08,0:12:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.42,0:12:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.15,0:12:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.72,0:12:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全聽不懂她的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.66,0:12:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.46,0:12:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好，我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.26,0:12:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她好像是在等某個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.33,0:12:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果把我誤認成那個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.06,0:12:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.13,0:12:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她要是不在那邊等那個人的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.10,0:12:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不就糟糕了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.97,0:12:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，在夏儂跟她說話以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.21,0:12:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道沒有人跟她說過話嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.64,0:12:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也蠻奇怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.85,0:12:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之等路面乾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.18,0:12:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再到那個鎮上去問問看好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.95,0:12:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來現在也只能這麼做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.34,0:12:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葛涅斯特霍克樞機卿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.31,0:13:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是克里斯多福．柏拉赫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.74,0:13:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柏拉赫？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.31,0:13:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位男爵夫人的兒子嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.05,0:13:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙您接見不勝感激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.62,0:13:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您身為瑪烏傑魯教會的樞機卿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.99,0:13:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又兼任殲滅部隊肅清使的總監
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.46,0:13:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有件事在下想要向您請教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.13,0:13:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒在下說話禮數不周
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.20,0:13:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我本來是\N專門從事破壞工作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.37,0:13:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特務戰技兵嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.00,0:13:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還曾經參與過兩次\N暗殺廢棄公主的計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.64,0:13:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以告訴在下呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.38,0:13:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於第5111次\N聖葛林德神諭的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.05,0:13:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真相？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.78,0:13:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你要問什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.25,0:13:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於當時的神諭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.39,0:13:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有留下\N任何直接的書面記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.43,0:13:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且神諭到現在為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.36,0:13:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經錯了兩次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.03,0:13:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有兩次而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.40,0:13:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該說居然有兩次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.13,0:14:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬能的神會犯兩次錯嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.40,0:14:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能是接收神諭的神官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.07,0:14:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在解釋時弄錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.27,0:14:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為神諭所用的語言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.91,0:14:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我們所用的不一樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.38,0:14:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我見過廢棄公主了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.95,0:14:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有你們稱為守護者的\N她的哥哥和姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.45,0:14:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.62,0:14:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再怎麼想\N都無法認為她是邪惡的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.29,0:14:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.13,0:14:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要把這種廢棄公主\N和塔爾斯鎮一起毀滅的神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.90,0:14:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.63,0:14:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得那次作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.27,0:14:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是由肅清使所策動的沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.47,0:14:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是神做下那種事的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.21,0:14:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.08,0:14:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了，今天就到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.65,0:14:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在下也許會再來拜訪\N向您請教一些問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.79,0:14:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時候請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.68,0:15:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼疲憊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.45,0:15:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史...史黛雅大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.45,0:15:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知您今日有何吩咐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.39,0:15:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要出去一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.76,0:15:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找人原本是葛里爾的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.46,0:15:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果他接手沒多久就死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.93,0:15:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道...大人他過世了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.50,0:15:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我會暫時離開一陣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.41,0:15:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的事情就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.24,0:15:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.94,0:15:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼身為神明使者的\N葛里爾大人會死呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.29,0:16:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.72,0:16:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.30,0:16:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳認為神應該是萬能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.60,0:16:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是絕對的存在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.71,0:16:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如神不是永遠不滅的存在...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.21,0:16:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.28,0:16:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然是神就不會死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.61,0:16:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為不會死亡所以才是神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.05,0:16:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正因為合乎正道所以不會死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.05,0:16:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使看起來像是死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.52,0:16:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也是神的意志所決定的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.29,0:16:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從最終的觀點來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.23,0:16:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神永遠都朝著正確的方向前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.50,0:16:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神是不會死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.77,0:16:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.77,0:16:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就先告退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.51,0:16:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真難喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.59,0:17:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.06,0:17:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要太過操勞我這個\N柔弱的少女，好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.73,0:17:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.10,0:17:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.07,0:17:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.07,0:17:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.47,0:17:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音真是個好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是好孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.44,0:17:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.15,0:17:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心別把裡面的餡掉出來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.85,0:17:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要這樣拿著吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.25,0:17:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.32,0:17:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.29,0:17:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.29,0:17:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，真是不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.76,0:17:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺就好像多了一個家人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.11,0:18:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.58,0:18:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳想幹嘛啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.48,0:18:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.45,0:18:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在夏儂哥在洗啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.58,0:18:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟夏儂一起洗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.75,0:18:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說妳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.82,0:18:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說妳也是個女孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.79,0:18:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡也要一起洗嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.19,0:18:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.99,0:18:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音喜歡夏儂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.30,0:18:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡也喜歡夏儂嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.57,0:18:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為夏儂哥是我哥哥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.37,0:18:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.74,0:18:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.05,0:18:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.41,0:18:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還有一條髮帶，對不對？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.89,0:18:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦，不要亂動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.45,0:18:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有會癢的地方了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.99,0:18:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.02,0:18:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那要沖水了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.23,0:18:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.67,0:19:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.94,0:19:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六、七
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.44,0:19:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.44,0:19:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.68,0:19:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以用跑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.75,0:19:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然她是個好孩子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.03,0:19:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉蔻兒姊，妳可以去洗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.43,0:19:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看，跟夏儂一樣的髮型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.07,0:19:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就來做一頓\N好久都沒嚐過的大餐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.80,0:19:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.21,0:19:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音也要幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.74,0:19:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，妳要來幫忙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.71,0:19:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟某個野丫頭完全不一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.25,0:19:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要做什麼菜？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.19,0:19:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以用魔法喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.54,0:20:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.34,0:20:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳叫賽菲莉絲對不對？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.44,0:20:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.04,0:20:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看來並不怕我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.31,0:20:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳姑且算是\N站在我們這一邊的，不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.62,0:20:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是被你們稱為魔族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.62,0:20:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擁有強大破壞力的存在喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.79,0:20:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是妳又不會對我們使用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.83,0:20:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我覺得沒什麼好怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.60,0:20:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點唐突\N不過我希望妳能協助我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.84,0:20:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,協助？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.47,0:20:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.78,0:20:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你們在一起的那個少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.98,0:20:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.05,0:20:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩音她怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.35,0:20:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺了那個少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.43,0:21:18.39,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,滋潤大地的雨水靜靜地飄下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.47,0:21:22.70,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,落在很遠很遠的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.71,0:21:31.08,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,將這愛的雨滴獻給 某個等待已久的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.15,0:21:36.78,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,清晨的微風吹過沾有雨滴的臉龐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.86,0:21:41.02,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,現在你感覺到什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.63,0:21:45.00,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,這雨滴有著明白的含意 比一切都還要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.07,0:21:49.53,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,就在那唯一的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.17,0:21:56.44,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,停駐在追趕著的雲影下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.51,0:22:00.24,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,在這心靈的旅程中想要找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.31,0:22:03.22,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,不管到哪裡不管到哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.28,0:22:09.95,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天會再聽到熟悉的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.02,0:22:16.66,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,船將會啟航啟航 船會航行到哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.73,0:22:22.00,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯要相信廣闊的世界 到未知的海洋的盡頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.07,0:22:28.84,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,你要前往遠方然後奔向未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.11,0:22:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽菲莉絲要求帕希菲卡殺死詩音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.05,0:22:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人無法得知在不知不覺之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.42,0:22:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有人對自己懷有惡意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.75,0:22:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了詩音\N夏儂和帕希菲卡吵了一架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.29,0:22:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄公主下一回\N「羈絆與祈禱的小夜曲」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.99,0:22:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待